size limits for group gatherings, the Office of International Services
will move all services online, effective March 17. Our office in SSB
will be closed to foot traffic until further notice. Read the full announcement with information on how to access services here .        Office Location    Office of International Services Student Services Building, 1200 West Harrison Street, Suite 2160 Chicago, IL 60607  MAP   Contact Information      Phone: 312-996-3121 Fax: 312-996-9432  Email: ois@uic.edu Email for newly admitted international students: newintl@uic.edu Email for F-1 students applying for and participating in the STEM OPT extension: stemopt@uic.edu   Staff Directory  Emergency Information  Social Media: Facebook , Twitter , Instagram  Office Mailing Address: Office of International Services (MC 326) Suite 2160 University of Illinois at Chicago Student Services Building 1200 West Harrison Street Chicago, IL 60607-7164   Service Hours  Front Desk  Monday - Friday, 8:30 a.m. - 5:00 p.m.  During this time, visitors may drop-off or pick-up documents, register for events, and ask general questions. Front desk staff are not able to advise on immigration regulations or specific cases.  Open Advising  Monday - Thursday, 10:30 a.m. - 3:30 p.m., Friday by appointment  Open Advising is a time for international students (F-1, J-1, other visa categories, and prospective students) and scholars (J-1 scholar, H-1B, O-1, etc.) to meet with an advisor to ask immigration-related or case-specific questions without a scheduled appointment. OIS Advisors are also available to discuss cultural adjustment issues and to assist with navigating UIC resources. Outside of Open Advising hours, an appointment is needed to meet with an advisor.    Immigration Check-in  International Students: Monday - Friday, 8:30 a.m. - 5:00 p.m.  J-1 Scholars: Mondays & Thursdays, 2:00 p.m. Please arrive at 2:00 p.m. with your immigration documents and proof of health insurance. If you are unable to attend the standard J-1 Scholar check-in time, please email ( ois@uic.edu ) or call (312-996-3121) to schedule an appointment.  H-1B & O-1: By appointment. Please email ( ois@uic.edu ) or call (312-996-3121) to schedule an appointment.  All other non-student scholars, visitors, and employees: Monday – Friday, 8:30 a.m. – 5:00 p.m. or via email to ois@uic.edu .  All new members of the UIC international community must visit OIS upon arrival to complete the Immigration Check-in. International students may find more information about the Immigration Check-in process and required documents here . J-1 Scholars may find more information here .        xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-16"? Skip Nav UICOIS Navigation Menu Home About OIS Executive Director's Welcome Our Population Staff Directory Hours and Location Emergency Information Spotlight on Scholars Students Faculty, Staff, and Scholars Visitors Departments Programs Life in Illinois Alumni Resources News   Office of International Services 1200 West Harrison Street Chicago, IL 60607-7161 Phone: (312) 996-3121 Email: ois@uic.edu Facebook Instagram Twitter Copyright ©  2018 The Board of Trustees of the University of Illinois | Web Privacy Statement Cookie Settings    